Big Brother 16 is the upcoming sixteenth season of the American reality television series Big Brother. The new season is scheduled to air on June 25, 2014 on CBS making it the earliest premiere date for a summer season Big Brother in the U.S. It will be the first season to be broadcast in high definition, the final television series to do so among the major broadcast networks (as Let's Make a Deal on CBS Daytime switched earlier for tapings beginning June 2014). The season premiere will be a two-night event, with the premiere episode airing on June 25 and the next episode airing on June 26.[/b]
